<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٤٦- مُحَمد بْن أَبي مُوسى.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ عَبد اللهِ بْنِ عَبد الرَّحمَن، عَنْ عليٍّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ شَرِيك:</span> لقيتُه بواسط.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لا يُصام يوم الشَّك.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>